Name: Cupid Story: First Date
About the game: Cupid Story is an RPG / dating sim in the Cupid Island universe. The cupid Noelia has a mission: get the human Daniel a girlfriend in 14 days. Too bad he's got no talent at all to make her job easier. FEATURES Classical turn-based RPG battle system Stronger relationships make for stronger characters Unlock new skills as the story progresses Dates are battles Choose the right girlfriend for Daniel from 3 unique girls This game is a prologue , it features the first episode of the complete Cupid Story .
